_aChangeLog.text: Removed trees to improve performance (they were ugly anyway)

_sText:
bhop_dusk is a map I made around this time 2 years ago but ended up scrapping. I have decided to upload the map again to tweak and make improvements to the map overtime.

Feel free to post suggestions in the comments as I may look into updating the map to make it longer or tweak some things.

Enjoy!

-Map by Alfex

Found some gameplay of the map if you are interested: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ijGVHzKiU_8
